{
  "stem": "14002.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They just opened up the-- the doors of the train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Down there we saw already civilians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I mean civilians, people from the-- from Auschwitz, with-- with concentration camp uniforms on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were Jews, of course.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say it was around the middle of the day, yeah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then down there, we saw SS soldiers with dogs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And next to my mother, where she stood in the line there, my mother with my sisters-- with my sister-- yeah, sisters too, Golde and Chaia.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a neighbor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She had twins.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She couldn't handle the twins.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were young, about a year, a year and a half old.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So my mother grabbed one, one of the children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And me, my father was in front of me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my brother was in the back of me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then there was that SS man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I think it was Mengele.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It looked like him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was standing there, like, with a small rod, pointing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He pointed my father to go to the right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But my father was born with a limp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "One leg was shorter with about an inch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The minute he started to walk to the right, he tapped him on the shoulder, pointed him to the left.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That was the last time I saw my father, without saying goodbye or anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was the last time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Of course, my mother took that child on her arm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I think that was a mistake of her side, because she went to the left.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because anybody what had a child, a young child, whatever it is, went to the left.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "My brother went with me, also the same.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We still don't know where-- didn't know where and what.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
